test_negate_of_divisors:
assert [6, 6, 6] == [6, 6]
  Left contains one more item: 6
  Full diff:
  - [6, 6]
  + [6, 6, 6]
  ?     +++
test_list_of_zeros:
assert [0, 0, 0] == [0, 0]
  Left contains one more item: 0
  Full diff:
  - [0, 0]
  + [0, 0, 0]
  ?     +++
test_coefficient_of_divisor:
assert [-30, -36] == [-36]
  At index 0 diff: -30 != -36
  Left contains one more item: -36
  Full diff:
  - [-36]
  + [-30, -36]
